\p
\v 12 Let \w me|strong="H3318"\w* tell \w you|strong="H3318"\w* \w about|strong="H3318"\w* Leviathan: \w its|strong="H3318"\w* powerful legs \w and|strong="H3318"\w* graceful proportions.  
