\v 23 \w Its|strong="H7760"\w* body is dense \w and|strong="H3220"\w* solid, \w as|strong="H7760"\w* \w if|strong="H7760"\w* \w it|strong="H7760"\w* is \w made|strong="H7760"\w* \w from|strong="H7760"\w* \w cast|strong="H7760"\w* metal.  
